            "type": "acg.display.html",
            "props": {
              "html": "<p>The recent rapid advancement of AI/LLM technology has introduced considerable confusion, disorientation, and with it alarming amounts of <strong>false promises</strong>, <strong>snake oil sales tactics</strong>, and <strong>sleazy shilling</strong>. Our duty as software professionals is to prevent such degradation of quality by insisting on a high watermark professional code of ethics.</p>"
